it's mostly a playground for gfx library

aand ppm image renderer and font renderer written with it


https://www3.nd.edu/~dthain/courses/cse20211/fall2013/gfx/


it supports most of upup syntax
it can draw .ppm images
it supports http / https (specify in config.h)

deps
====

imagemagick, libcurl and libx11

usage
=====

	git clone https://github.com/krzysckh/webb
	cd webb
	make -j$(nproc)
	./webb -h

fonts
=====

adding a font:
	cd fonts
	./webbfont /path/to/font.[ttf/otf] > _Font_Name.frfont
	./webb -f fonts/_Font_Name.frfont


[ krzysckh 2022 ]

